.Dd June 2, 2026
.Dt PLAY 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm play
.Nd play one Matroska chapter through PulseAudio
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar path
.Ar chapter-id
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is the private playback helper used by
.Xr musicd 1 .
It opens the Matroska file at
.Ar path ,
locates
.Ar chapter-id ,
and writes the chapter audio to the default PulseAudio sink.
.Pp
.Nm
responds to signals from
.Xr musicd 1 :
.Bl -tag -width SIGUSR2 -compact
.It Dv SIGHUP
Stop playback.
.It Dv SIGUSR1
Resume playback.
.It Dv SIGUSR2
Pause playback.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr musicd 1
